British Airways Plc &lt;BAB.L> is issuing a100 mln stg eurobond due May 6, 1997, paying 9-1/2 pct andpriced at 101-1/2, lead manager Union Bank of Switzerland said.    The non-callable bond is available in denominations of1,000 and 10,000 stg and will be listed in London. The sellingconcession is 1-1/4 pct while management and underwritingcombined pays 3/4 pct.    Payment date is May 6. REUTER&#3;